services:
AGM Renovations offers Complete basement and Bathroom renovations packages from the professional design through the professional cleaning including:

Drywall- We employ only professional drywall installers and our goal is deliver complete satisfaction to each and every client with the quality of our workmanship and our prompt, reliable service.
    
Taping- Our drywall taping techniques will bring a high quality smooth finish, with a level of excellence you will take pride in.

Painting- We include all wall priming, painting of ceilings, baseboards, casing, crown and cove moldings into our basement construction packages
    
High Grade Laminate Flooring- is standard in our basement renovations packages.

Tiling- Shower, bathroom, or kitchenette tiling will be done by professional tile installers who are employed directly by AGM. A 2 year unlimited warranty is provided to you standard when you finish your basement with AGM
   
Plumbing- Our licensed plumbers will ensure that no problem is left unsolved and you can be sure that any drain or other plumbing defects left by the original house builder will be fixed effectively.

Electrical- We are committed to providing fully licensed electrician service as part of our standard package. Should you ever require an electrical certificate when you decide to sell your property, we will be happy to provide it to you

profile:
Why choose The Renovators of Canada?  
 
For over the past 20 years our focus on customer experience has helped The Renovators of Canada grow to locations in Durham, Aurora, Stouffville, Markham, Vaughan, Toronto, Hamilton, Guelph, Kitchener, Waterloo, Barrie, Oshawa, Oakville and Cambridge. 
 
Unique to the industry, The Renovators of Canada provides a 10 year warranty on all craftsmanship. This home renovation warranty protection was established to provide peace of mind as home and business owners contemplate renovating a personal or commercial space. 
 
T-ROC is a fully licensed and insured including WSIB. Other affiliations include memberships with the National Kitchen and Bath Association, CARAHS, Better Business Bureau.  
 
We have a proven track record working with our customers with full transparency in every aspect of your project.  Can’t be present all the time during the renovation process?  No worries, we have specialized client software that allows you to see the entire schedule and pictures as the project happens in real time. We care for your home like it’s our own and always conduct ourselves respectfully and professionally.  
 
With our motivated and innovative professionals we will transform your house and make your dream home a reality.  Visit our website at www.trocanada.com

profile:
Need a Handy Man?
​If you are looking for and need a handyman, no problem, we have you looked after!  No project is too small, no project is too large for the Handyman Service Experts.  We are your best option and can handle all your construction needs when it comes to repairs and renovations.
 
Handyman Service Experts specialize in general tasks including everyday carpentry, home repairs, mounting and hanging, kitchen cabinet repairs, drywall, painting minor electrical, plumbing and so much more.  If you don’t have the expertise, tools, or just simply the time, we are here for you and will be right at your door to help.

Our service area is the County of Simcoe and surrounding area, however, we have been know to go further for our special customers that love our work!

Our Process:
As easy as 1, 2, 3...
 
First, a free telephone consultation to confirm the details of your project. Second, we will provide you with a rough estimate of the project.  And third, arrange for what you need and when you need it taken care of.

Estimate:
 
We can offer our hourly rate of 65.00/hour or we can provide a free estimate of services required. Before getting started, our handyman will review the scope of work with you. We want no surprises, so no work begins until you sign off on the estimate and are satisfied with every aspect of the project.
​
The Project: 
 
We will arrive with the tools to do the job. If you haven’t already purchased the materials, and request that we do this, we can take care of this for you. Our handyman approach is that every project is done with the attention to detail and not just to the project details, but also to the safety, security, and cleanliness of the rest of your home and all of your belongings.
​
Full Home Check-up:
 
Before leaving your premises, our handyman will offer you a a full home check-up. This is a complimentary service that we offer to all of our customers. You are in no way obliged to accept it. We will review key areas of home maintenance for you and give you an overview that may require attention.
​
Finalizing:

As we charge by the hour and have a 2 hour minimum for any work after 2 hours falls under standard rates. If we gave you an estimate, then we stand by that agreed upon estimate and is the amount that will be required for payment of our services. Any additional services will first be agreed upon, and be handled as a separate estimate and any payments required will be separate from the original estimate. Payment for the services are due once the work has been completed.

Thank you, and we look forward to hearing from you to get the job done!

JPG Contracting is a general contractor providing professional construction management for new home construction, custom homes, home renovations, additions, home improvements, plumbing, decking, and installing siding. Proudly serving the Muskoka and Surrounding Regions with only the best home improvement services.


 At JPG Contracting, which is located in Bracebridge, we build and renovate quality homes with a reputation for quality and service. Our attention to detail and high quality is recognized by professionals and homeowners alike. 

JPGs promise and commitment to you is simple. We will: 

Always do high-quality work at a fair price 

Complete your project on-time and on-budget to your satisfaction 

Only use environmentally friendly construction methods and materials 

Take detailed precautions to respect and protect your home/cottage 

Meet or exceed all workplace safety standards while on your site

One of a kind.
Your project is one of a kind. It is completely you and personalized. It is your dreams come to life. Through harmonious design, detailing, and craftsmanship, we help turn your dreams into a reality. 

 	 
Inspired Dreams.
We are here to work with you! Your ideas inspire us. Our job is to take your vision and dream and carefully execute it through clear communication concepts. We will also identify smart home improvements, potential issues, budgeting, and inspections through every step of the process. 


Become Reality.
We use our attention to detail, so that you are pleased with the results. We are here to answer any questions you have through all the stages of the process. This is what makes us exceptional! We care about our customers, and will work to make your dreams a reality. 

A renovation, or full build is a multi stage project. It requires organization, dedication, and timelines. At JPG Contracting, our trusted team of professionals will deliver you beautiful results. We pride ourselves on organization, communication, precise work, and craftsmanship.
